comments: Reddish (ATL) engages and disengages with Brown (BOS) along the perimeter.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Smart (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.

Hayward (BOS) reflexively places his arms around Len's (ATL) midsection as the pick is set and quickly removes them.

Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Young's (ATL) path and does not deliver the contact.
Hayward (BOS) hedges the pick and makes some contact with both hands to Young's (ATL) side/front, but it is marginal.

Hayward (BOS) makes marginal contact with Len's (ATL) left arm during rebounding that does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball and attempt the ensuing putback.
